						<summary>

						<p>This is an incomplete inscription. It records an endowment of a quarter <hi rend="italic">s11ey</hi> of land as <hi rend="italic">s11ālaippuṟam</hi>, left in charge of the <hi rend="italic">ūrār</hi> of the village for the celebration of the annual Kārttigai festival in the temple of Tiruvaṟappaḷḷiyāḻvār by <hi rend="bold">Pratigaṇḍaṉ Darachchōḻaṉ.</hi> Probably a record of <hi rend="bold">Uttama-Chōḷa.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
